    <item>
      <title>美国立法者达成协议，让政府保持开放至 9 月 30 日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/us-lawmakers-reach-deal-to-keep-government-open-through-sept-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在长达六个月的激烈意识形态冲突导致年度支出计划推迟完成后，国会领​​导人和白宫达成了一项握手协议，为国家政府提供资金至 9 月 30 日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/us-lawmakers-reach-deal-to-keep-government-open-through-sept-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 01:25:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AMLO 准备接管墨西哥玛雅里维埃拉的 Vulcan 财产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/amlo-prepares-to-take-over-vulcan-property-in-mexico-s-mayan-riviera</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，经过多年谈判未能达成购买该地产的协议后，墨西哥政府正准备控制 Vulcan Materials Co. 拥有的位于该国加勒比海岸的采石场和港口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/amlo-prepares-to-take-over-vulcan-property-in-mexico-s-mayan-riviera</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 00:30:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
