    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织将提供接近创纪录的 1500 亿美元贷款来应对债务和战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/imf-lending-near-record-150-billion-to-counter-debt-and-wars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织正在向近 100 个国家提供接近创纪录金额的贷款，这证明其在应对大流行后世界的金融和政治危险方面的作用日益增强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/imf-lending-near-record-150-billion-to-counter-debt-and-wars</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:43:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>面对 Milei 的乐观情绪，Enel 暂停出售阿根廷 Edesur</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/enel-suspended-sale-of-argentina-s-edesur-amid-milei-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利能源巨头 Enel SpA 发言人表示，该公司周一证实，由于公司高管对总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 放松该行业监管的努力抱有希望，该公司已暂停在阿根廷出售子公司电力分销商 Edesur。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/enel-suspended-sale-of-argentina-s-edesur-amid-milei-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:40:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普排除维韦克·拉马斯瓦米作为竞选伙伴，因为他正在寻找新团队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/trump-rules-out-ramaswamy-as-running-mate-as-he-eyes-new-team</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)已经排除了维韦克·拉马斯瓦米(Vivek Ramaswamy)作为他的竞选搭档，转而关注这位企业家担任内阁职务，这位共和党总统候选人正在评估可能的政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/trump-rules-out-ramaswamy-as-running-mate-as-he-eyes-new-team</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:32:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
