      <title>亨特·拜登拒绝出席本周的公共众议院听证会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/hunter-biden-refuses-to-appear-at-public-house-hearing-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登拒绝了在国会公开听证会上作证的邀请，该听证会涉及商业活动，而商业活动是共和党对其父亲、总统乔·拜登弹劾调查的焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/hunter-biden-refuses-to-appear-at-public-house-hearing-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 23:27:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俱乐部谈判陷入僵局后英国将制定足球监管法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/uk-to-set-out-football-regulation-law-after-club-talks-stall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国将立法设立独立的足球监管机构，在顶级英超联赛和低级别英格兰足球联赛之间重新分配收入，政府将进行干预，努力保障小型俱乐部的财务可持续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/uk-to-set-out-football-regulation-law-after-club-talks-stall</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
